      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Businessman Jonathan Martenstyn and swimming champion Julian Bolling have been summoned to the CID tomorrow (17), over July 9th Protests.",
        "The Criminal Investigations Department said that they are being summoned to record statements for the future investigation on the incident where President Ranil Wickremesinghe's house was torched on the 9th of July.",
